Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,but also we loved you\Nfrom the beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.55,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,so we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] A bear has crossed\Nthe Wall of Severance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,our only line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tragically, Sumika Izumino\Nlost her life to that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,At this time,\Nwe have been unable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.70,Main,,0,0,0,,to reach Katyusha Akae\Nand Konomi Yurikawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:15.16,Main,,0,0,0,,along with several other\Nstudents from our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,The fact is, we face\Nour greatest crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,since the Day of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That being said, a bear\Nwas shot last night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,that we believe to\Nhave been the invader,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,but we mustn't let\Nour guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's important for\Nyou all to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,that the friends\Nsitting next to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,are the keys to your\Nprotection from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Never be alone for a moment,\Neven on school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ladies, you must\Nprotect each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Don't worry.\NI'll be the one to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But why not?\NWhat about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday? I think\Nyou got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:11.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, be that way.\NIt's your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Damn it.\NShe rejected me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, though.\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth is I kind of\Nlike this side of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The fun's only beginning,\NKureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna work\Nyou over real good,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.77,Main,,0,0,0,,and then I'll eat\Nyou right on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] How are you?\NHave you calmed down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NLiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] You're not\Nvery good at it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:20.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia was like that,\Ntoo, honest to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NReia? You mean my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,My, you remind me of that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,So much like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] You mustn't\Nsuffer in silence, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The more you try to hide the\Npain of losing a loved one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,the more that pain will grow\Nand become unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I know\Nthis all too well myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother? I lost\NReia that day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She was such a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.96,Main,,0,0,0,,She was my best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:59.47,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'll never have another\Nlike her again. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I was so happy\Nwhen you came to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:05.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And when you decided to bring\Nthe flowerbed back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,it touched my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,that place held special\Nmemories for Reia and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI hate bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYes, so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, they took the ones\Nwe loved away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,There's another bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,There's another bear\Nstill out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But how? Wasn't the bear that\Nattacked Sumika taken care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought your friend\NMitsuko killed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She only killed one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw them! Two bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm positive it's in this\Nschool. It has to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,That bear is somewhere close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NThis school set up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.27,Main,,0,0,0,,really is an excellent\Nsystem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is\Nhang out here for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,and wait for the right\Nopportunity to present itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO]\NHey, Mitsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I was thinking since\NKonomi's missing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,that maybe I could\Nfill in for her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea, Eriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Class friendship\Nnaturally starts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,with individual\Nresponsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The leadership you're showing\Nis awesome. Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Strong people\Nare beautiful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO]\NUh, thank you, Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.72,Main,,0,0,0,,We should be best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Yuri ga aku. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:36.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] There's my good girl.\NI can't waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to eat Kureha Tsubaki\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,There's one more bear.\NI know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'll never forgive the bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin them. Every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[gunshots continue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl. Look at that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,She's totally itching\Nto shoot a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This sucks, the only reason\Nwe came here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.11,Main,,0,0,0,,was to beat that sticky,\Nicky Mitsuko Yurizono
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,to the dinner punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But we can't get\Nclose to her, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,So stupid. Who knew there'd be\Na rival bear at that school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Punch, punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Saw through our disguises,\Ntoo! Punch, punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, jeez. You're so not even\Nlistening to me, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki must\Nbe the tastiest girl
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,in the whole world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER] Pope Urban the\NSecond's moving sermon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,at the Council of Clermont\Nproved to be highly effective,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,summoning the armies\Nof kings and nobility
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,across most of Western Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This effort formed the first\Narmy of crusaders in 1096.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Thus began a long\Nseries of wars
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,in an attempt to regain the\NHoly Land from the Seljuk Turks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, I think you\Nforgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER] All right, girls,\Nguess what will be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NPlease, not this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER]\NAre you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not just talking\Nto hear myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NOh, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.86,Main,,0,0,0,,The time moves so slowly when\Nyou're not in class with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER] What this means\Nis that the Crusades
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,exposed the people\Nof Western Europe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.66,Main,,0,0,0,,to the drastically different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Will I start\Nto forget everything now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Forget that day, that moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Will I eventually forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,and be invisible\Njust like everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NYour mother's flowerbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Yeah, mom told me that\Nback when she was a student here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,she built it with her\Nbest friend at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NAh, so that's why you love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course. I want to fill it\Nwith lots of flowers again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,because I think she'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet. You didn't\Ngive up on her love either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NYour mother's precious garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like your love for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhh. Like my love how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm not\Ngonna give up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Not on you. Not on my\Nprecious love. Our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika, I swear I'll\Nnever give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Attention, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Above all things we\Nmust remain invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The time has come to begin\Nthe Exclusion Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends are more important\Nthan anything else, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The friends here in this\Nclassroom right now are Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We are Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who dare to\Ncontradict Our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,are nothing but a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,As are those who want to\Nstick out from our crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The ones that refuse to\Nfit in with Us are a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:34.76,Main,,0,0,0,,People like that, those who\Ndon't follow social cues
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino\Nwas eaten by a bear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,because she was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only natural, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,People who are evil get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We're here to decide who\Nthat next evil will be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,so we can exclude them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NSelect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The moment has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat that girl.\NKureha, you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww, you really love her,\Ndon't you, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] I want you to know as\Nlong as you don't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never, ever be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Just remember that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't forget about love,\NI won't really be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANCHORWOMAN] That's correct,\Na storm and flood warning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,has just been issued for\Nthe greater metro area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,We're seeing\Nviolent rain and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Residents in the\Nfollowing districts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,have been advised to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,If this applies to you,\Nevacuate immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I gotta\Nprotect the flowerbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You came out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NAren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] I'm perfect\Nsince you're here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI, um, I just wanna say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...thank you, for being\Nmy friend, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, and thanks\Nfor being mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:51.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I won't do it.\NI won't back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NTo live is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:14:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,One must continually forget,\Nback down, and cast away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[scissors snip]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Those who cannot\Nreplace the old with the new
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,will eventually perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Beasts like us never live\Nin the past, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The only thing that\Nexists is the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Emotions we feel in the now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The mood, the rhythm of this\Nmoment. That is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] The invisible ones\Nthink they're in control,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,but they can only decide\Nhow to run closed worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NOh, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu will never forget the\Nwonderful day she met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That was when you found her\Nlove. You brought it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu won't ever give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems the time for\Njudgment has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYou bet it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] This is a challenge\Nfrom the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki,\Nif your love is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,go to the roof immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Give yourself over to the bears,\Nand your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'll never forgive the bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin them. Every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] I've been waiting\Nfor you, my dear Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Mitsuko?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Getting ready\Nto eat you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NSo, I've got some information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,you might want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who ate your\Nbeloved Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a big bad bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] This is probably\Nhard for you to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,but it is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,To be specific, I'm a bear who's\Njust pretending to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NA bear pretending to be human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You got it! Wanna know\Nwho that bear I shot was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Konomi Yurikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NKonomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I thought she was your--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose\Ntechnically she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She obeyed me at least, and\Nthat was pretty swell of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Let me give you\Na piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're deciding\Nto be friends with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.19,Main,,0,0,0,,it's imperative to\Nmake sure the lucky girl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,is just a little bit\Ninferior to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,They're always so much\Neasier to control that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to look so\Nincredulous. Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If you need proof I'm telling\Nthe truth, I can give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, those are Sumika's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. I take it\Nyou finally believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you,\Nthat girl was a freak job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, there she was,\Nliterally being eaten alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,and yet, all she did\Nwas worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NI'm sorry. Oh, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't fix your love now,\Nor your mother's flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,And I promised I wouldn't\Nback down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you can forgive me\None day, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm so, so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:19.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, as if you\Nhave it in you to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that rage there in your\Neyes is the reason I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.97,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's really starting\Nto get me off. So hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And your blood, I can\Nsense it furiously boiling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,its way through your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Your scent is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I can hardly stand what\NI'm smelling off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, get angrier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive the bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:48.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin them.\NI swear. Every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I already said it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You simply don't have\Nit in you to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NGrawr, grawr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Grararawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:05.71,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--Such bad aim.\N--[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Missed me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--What a shock,\N--[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--you missed me again.\N--[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You keep missing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Rawr, rawr, rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Don't worry. I have a\Nplan to make everything better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] In place of the\NSumika I ate, I'll love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:30.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NWe want to eat that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,We want to eat her\Nright this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NThis court is now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLet the Yuri Trial begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Your Honor,\Nwe need Yuri approval, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to save Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You say you want to\Nsave Kureha Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,well, that hardly makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? You two are bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. We will still\Neat humans, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If we don't eat them,\Nwe can't protect Ginko's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you're blatantly\Nadmitting your crime
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,in a court of law, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha. Damn it, I'm cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely you realize for a bear,\Neating humans is hardly a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NPlease rule quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to save her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,For that is sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant bears, I ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Or would you rather eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring on the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NGrowl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] I am now ready\Nto declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:20:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NYuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Growly, growl, growl,\Ngrowly, growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI won't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't back down\Non your love, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We know the truth. Only love\Ncan change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Love can change the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:06.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Their tongues feel rough,\Nbut they're also warm and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I've felt this\Nbefore, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NSmooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Give it to me,\Nthe Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NGrawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:33.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NGrawrr-rr-rrr-rr-rr!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI hit her. I think--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be! A bear\Nin human form. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[gun clatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO] What did you\Nwant to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:09.95,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's the Exclusion Ceremony,\NI'm sorry, but no can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You aren't allowed\Nto participate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,because you can't be our friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,until you take part\Nin the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:16.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI don't want to. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So instead, we'll tell you\Nsomething you'll want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,How's that sound, Eriko Oniyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:23.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO]\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NFirst answer this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Where do you think\Nyour missing friends are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO] Missing friends?\NYou mean like Katyusha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NThey're right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[ERIKO]\NI don't-- What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.65,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the place we\Nburied Katyusha Akae.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, the parts we didn't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NAren't we the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that... that you\Nate her? You ate my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Why tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Because guess what\Nwe're gonna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:02.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:05.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
